Early Access Review
								Funny and entertaining. It's generally humorous, and the player quests are a definite plus point. Not exactly the MMO genre I was expecting, but yeah it's still somewhat fun at least. I'd say this /does/ deserve a try, the game develeoper(s) have put a good bit of effort in the humorous elements. For me, 'Not bad'. ^^;

